node.text:
Get back to whatever makes you feel like you – in style, of course – with these adorable PINK pieces! 💗 In honor of our Back To ____ campaign, we’re giving FIVE lucky winners this package filled with PINK product!
 
Here’s how to enter:
 
1. Follow us @VSPINK
2. Like this post
3. Tag a friend in the comments below with the hashtag #PINKSweepstakes
 
No purch nec. US res only, age of maj. Ends at 11:59 P.M. ET on 8/27/2021Void where prohibited. (Not void in New Jersey). See rules [bit.ly/3D7bPfA]. Review Victoria’s Secret’s Privacy Policy and Financial Incentives Privacy Notice (for California residents) (also included in the Official Rules) (both at [bit.ly/2PojjTN]) and California Privacy Rights Notice (at [bit.ly/3guVKET]).
